node.text:
…..is somehow oddly satisfying. Seasoned with The Gospel AP. Smoked on the @traegergrills at 250° with hickory. Wrapped around 175° internal when the bark was perfect looking. Topped with brown sugar, Honey Hog Hot & butter in the wrap. Pulled when it was probe tender. 

#MeatChurch #TexasBBQ #PulledPork #TheGospel #Gospel

node.text:
Thank you to our friends @mirandalambert, @brendanjmcloughlin & @db102681 for inviting us to spend the weekend with them. This was the first time our new @mill.scale has fed people other than ourselves & video. The new pit needed a name. As with all things Meat Church I want to cut my own path and not be anybody else. (There are like 2,000 pits named Dolly). I needed a new unique name. We chose Geraldene. A song written and performed on the Marfa Tapes by the crazy talented trio @mirandalambert, @jackingram & @jonrandallmusic in a raw, rustic basically unedited session in Marfa, TX. This pit is raw, patina steel and fed it’s first meal to this trio in New Braunfels, TX this weekend. I knew the name and story would come to me at the right time and this is perfect. 

“You're trailer park pretty, but you're never gonna be Jolene.”

Great hangs with Miranda, Brendan, Dustin, Jack, Jon (swipe ➡️ to see em) & crew. Geraldene can’t wait to feed y’all again!

#MeatChurch #TexasBBQ #MirandaLambert #Geraldene #MarfaTapes

📸: @acaciaevans
